videos.description: Jacques Patrick sprints through the middle of the Wake Forest defense for 69 yards in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Patrick gives the Seminoles some breathing room with 69-yard run

videos.description: Wake Forest's Grant Dawson strips Florida State wide receiver George Campbell  as the Demon Deacons get their first turnover of the game.
videos.headline: Wake Forest defense forces turnover

videos.description: Amari Henderson puts a big hit on Nyqwan Murray as the Demon Deacon defense dominates in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Henderson drills Florida State wide receiver

videos.description: Wake Forest quarterback John Wolford takes it in from three yards out for the game's first touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford keeps it himself for the TD

videos.description: Mike Weaver responds to the Demon Deacons' touchdown with a big kick return to shift the momentum.
videos.headline: Florida State's Weaver takes kickoff 62 yards to the Wake Forest 19-yard line

videos.description: Jacques Patrick pounds it in for the one-yard score in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Patrick bullies his way in for TD

videos.description: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher gives a brief overview of how the Seminoles will improve in the second half.
videos.headline: Jimbo gives his thoughts on the first half

videos.description: James Blackman is sacked by Willie Yarbary in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Wake Forest DT enters backfield unblocked for sack

videos.description: Quarterback John Wolford fumbles the snap but completes the pass which is fumbled and recovered by Florida State.
videos.headline: Wake Forest offense loses ball after a complete meltdown

videos.description: John Wolford eludes two defenders to keep the play alive finding Cam Sergine to extend the drive in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Wolford escapes the sack,  connects with TE for 1st down

videos.description: Matt Colburn takes the lead back for the Demon Deacons with a seven-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Colburn gives Wake Forest the lead with TD in the 4th

videos.description: James Blackman connects with Auden Tate for the 40-yard touchdown pass to take the lead late in the fourth.
videos.headline: Blackman throws long TD pass with under a minute to go in 4th

videos.description: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher talks about his young stars stepping up in their big 26-19 win over Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Fisher on his freshman quarterback coming up big in win

videos.description: Tommy Tuberville and Mike Patrick break down Florida State's late game heroics to secure the 26-19 win.
videos.headline: Seminoles earn first win of the season
